## Typography tokens (reference — get exact values from Figma Dev Mode)

```
Headings:   Noto Serif JP (Mincho/serif)
Body & UI:  Noto Sans JP (Gothic/sans-serif)
Max families: 3 total (do not add a third family without discussion)

Line heights:
  Body:     1.8–2.0
  Headings: 1.4–1.5

Recommended desktop sizes:
  H1:             48–56px
  Section heading: 32–40px
  Subheading:     20–24px
  Body:           16–17px (minimum 16px including mobile)
  Secondary:      13–14px
  English labels: 10–11px, letter-spacing: 0.15em

Hover: opacity 0.7 on buttons, links, and images (designer spec).
```

